    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/5d241fc3e29102814e8f47358077998c.poster.avif?t=1772105218\" width=800 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/5d241fc3e29102814e8f47358077998c.webm?t=1772105218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/5d241fc3e29102814e8f47358077998c.mp4?t=1772105218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heartweaver is a 3D puzzle adventure game about loss and healing. Follow the journey of Ace and Mark through Ace's twisted mind and help them reconnect with their feelings. Explore beautiful dark worlds that bring Ace's psyche to life, use their emotions to solve puzzles, recover their memories and help them weave a path towards healing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ㅤ</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/599c53f46ad7820c96a21a1d0ad6a3d9.avif?t=1772105218\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras_big/599c53f46ad7820c96a21a1d0ad6a3d9.avif?t=1772105218 width=800 height=201 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Ace free their repressed emotions. Connect through their feelings with their mental blocks and dissolve them.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/2ea63b8598bdf928c2298327e11861a3.poster.avif?t=1772105218\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/2ea63b8598bdf928c2298327e11861a3.webm?t=1772105218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/2ea63b8598bdf928c2298327e11861a3.mp4?t=1772105218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ㅤ</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/6ac4ff466ab5aac6b8a927869f71c46f.avif?t=1772105218\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras_big/6ac4ff466ab5aac6b8a927869f71c46f.avif?t=1772105218 width=800 height=201 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rearrange Ace's confused mind. Solve puzzles to clear their thoughts and see things clearly. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/2f6c9c743c3b39885e15d05ad7c23e48.poster.avif?t=1772105218\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/2f6c9c743c3b39885e15d05ad7c23e48.webm?t=1772105218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/2f6c9c743c3b39885e15d05ad7c23e48.mp4?t=1772105218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ㅤ</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/a27d99f9525fceeae772f14ce202deba.avif?t=1772105218\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras_big/a27d99f9525fceeae772f14ce202deba.avif?t=1772105218 width=800 height=201 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move forward by using the abilities of Ace's sadness, fear and anger. Let Ace get so sad it slows down time, make their spirit leave their body from the fright and push things far away in a burst of rage.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/99ff14431c69d5587029b9ad829c05f6.poster.avif?t=1772105218\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/99ff14431c69d5587029b9ad829c05f6.webm?t=1772105218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/99ff14431c69d5587029b9ad829c05f6.mp4?t=1772105218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ㅤ</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/8dc26a40e206171eef05a2a4849b9ee9.avif?t=1772105218\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras_big/8dc26a40e206171eef05a2a4849b9ee9.avif?t=1772105218 width=800 height=201 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover Ace's story by travelling through the distorted worlds of their mind. Make the journey alongside Mark and explore every nook and cranny.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/739ff47b8f5c073524a0de6afbd3bd73.poster.avif?t=1772105218\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/739ff47b8f5c073524a0de6afbd3bd73.webm?t=1772105218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/739ff47b8f5c073524a0de6afbd3bd73.mp4?t=1772105218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ㅤ</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/fd3166084aaf07e1c4e5a9bb2eb0d3b5.avif?t=1772105218\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras_big/fd3166084aaf07e1c4e5a9bb2eb0d3b5.avif?t=1772105218 width=800 height=201 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Ace heal from their pain by recovering pieces of their past. Collect tokens from Ace's memories and make them remember their past.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/04a1620b1956bf14bdcf172fb1a07709.poster.avif?t=1772105218\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/04a1620b1956bf14bdcf172fb1a07709.webm?t=1772105218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/04a1620b1956bf14bdcf172fb1a07709.mp4?t=1772105218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ㅤ</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras/1bd3785f8ac11f18ff240140e03ff73f.avif?t=1772105218\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114600/extras_big/1bd3785f8ac11f18ff240140e03ff73f.avif?t=1772105218 width=800 height=213 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Companion</p>